rows.label: qst400205_msg0002
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Uh-oh. Maybe it wasn't a good idea
to ask an Superbian soldier...

rows.label: qst400205_msg0003
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Um, there was something I wanted
to ask, but now I've clean forgotten
what it was!

rows.label: qst400205_msg0004
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Actually, asking an Superbian soldier
may not have been the best plan...

rows.label: qst400205_msg0005
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]There was something I wanted to ask,
but actually, I'm sure you're busy!

rows.label: qst400205_msg0006
rows.name:
Hmph... If it's information you're after,
go pay for it at a local informant.

rows.label: qst400205_msg0007
rows.name:
Chatting with the populace isn't
our job, you understand.
